    {
      "instruction": "<p>While everything is cooking top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> apple<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (skin on) into matchsticks</p><p>Wash the <strong>gem lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p>",
      "order": 4,
